snippet.title: I turned We Don't Talk About Bruno into an anime opening song - Japanese Metal
snippet.description:
Hi everyone! Welcome to my We Don't Talk About Bruno anime opening! The full Version! This is a fan reimagining that turns We Don't Talk About Bruno into an anime opening banger! It is also a metal version/cover of We Don't Talk about Bruno. It is set to Jojo's Bizarre adventure just cause I thought the vibe would fit. I hope Encanto and anime fans enjoy this Encanto/We Don't Talk About Bruno inspired anime opening I created for the movie! 

My spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/5VbmUJRJhxLOYSNvKFpAUT
